    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>cornflour</strong>,<strong> ground smoked paprika </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> to a plate and mix it all together</p><p>Pat your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Press the <strong>basa </strong>firmly into the <strong>seasoned flour</strong>, coating evenly on both sides – this is your <strong>coated basa</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
