            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>mayo</strong> to a small with the <strong>grated garlic</strong>, <strong>remaining cider vinegar</strong>,<strong> dried oregano</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>ranch-style mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
